Introduction

loba means : speak, or talk. 
It's translated from one of the Congo Republic languages called Lingala.
loba provides a simple way to connect to irc.
It's a basic client, with QML design front end.

How to build on Linux

create a directory called bin in the root directory. Execute :
$ cmake ..
$ make

